{"id":1757,"date":"2024-09-14T19:30:43","date_gmt":"2024-09-14T19:30:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1757"},"modified":"2024-09-14T19:30:43","modified_gmt":"2024-09-14T19:30:43","slug":"lopunnite","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/lopunnite\/","title":{"rendered":"Lopunnite"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Lopunnite (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Gift from the Crush Kin trainers on an island on Route 2 after defeating them. Requires Surf to reach.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Lopunny<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Dresco Town<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Defeat every trainer on Route 2<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Dresco Town Pok\u00e9mon Center and start going west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lopunnite\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-dresco-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Dresco Town Pok\u00e9mon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Dresco Town Pok\u00e9mon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Turn south after reaching the island with the Dresco Town Gym and continue following the path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lopunnite\/02-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-path-south-of-the-gym.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the path south of the gym. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the path south of the gym.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually reach a piece of land closer to the water. Use Surf and start going east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lopunnite\/03-pokemon-unbound-using-surf-to-go-east.jpg\" alt=\"Using Surf to go east. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Surf to go east.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Hug the edge of the island to your north until you can go up. <\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lopunnite\/04-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-1st-turn-north.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the first turn north. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the first turn north.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Swim under the blue bridge and follow the path going northeast.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lopunnite\/05-pokemon-unbound-going-northeast-after-swimming-under-the-bridge.jpg\" alt=\"Going northeast after swimming under the bridge. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going northeast after swimming under the bridge.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually see a rocky island you can land on using some stairs.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lopunnite\/06-pokemon-unbound-climbing-the-rocky-island.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing the rocky island. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climbing the rocky island.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Interact with the two trainers on the rocky island and they\u2019ll challenge you to a battle if you\u2019ve beaten every other trainer on Route 2.<\/p>\n<p>The two trainers will give you the Lopunite when you defeat them.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lopunnite\/07-pokemon-unbound-about-to-challenge-the-2-trainers-on-top-of-the-island.jpg\" alt=\"About to challenge the two trainers on top of the island. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>About to challenge the two trainers on top of the island.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\">\n<table class=\"table grey left\" style=\"min-width:750px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"5\" class=\"text-large\">Crush Kin trainers<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/lopunnite\/08-pokemon-unbound-crush-kin-trainers.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100px;\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/pokemon\/hitmonlee.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/pokemon\/mega-lopunny.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/pokemon\/hawlucha.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/pokemon\/mega-lopunny.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Pok\u00e9mon<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>Hitmonlee (Level 52 at Big Mo cap)<\/td>\n<td>Mega Lopunny (Level 53 at Big Mo cap)<\/td>\n<td>Hawlucha (Level 52 at Big Mo cap)<\/td>\n<td>Mega Lopunny (Level 53 at Big Mo cap)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Type<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>Fighting<\/td>\n<td>Normal\/Fighting<\/td>\n<td>Fighting\/Flying<\/td>\n<td>Normal\/Fighting<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Ability<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>Limber<\/td>\n<td>Cute Charm &#8211; Scrappy<\/td>\n<td>Limber<\/td>\n<td>Klutz &#8211; Scrappy<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Held Item<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>Black Belt<\/td>\n<td>Lopunnite<\/td>\n<td>Black Belt<\/td>\n<td>Lopunnite<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Weaknesses<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Flying (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Psychic (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fighting (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Flying (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Psychic (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Flying (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Electric (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Psychic (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Ice (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Fighting (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Flying (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Psychic (2x)<\/li>\n<li>Fairy (2x)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Moves<\/strong><\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Close Combat<\/li>\n<li>Blaze Kick<\/li>\n<li>Rock Slide<\/li>\n<li>Wide Guard<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Dizzy Punch<\/li>\n<li>Jump Kick<\/li>\n<li>Thunder Punch<\/li>\n<li>Fake Out<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Flying Press<\/li>\n<li>Sky Drop<\/li>\n<li>Rock Slide<\/li>\n<li>Quick Guard<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Dizzy Punch<\/li>\n<li>Jump Kick<\/li>\n<li>Brutal Swing<\/li>\n<li>Fake Out<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Mega Stones<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1758,"parent":278,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[12],"class_list":["post-1757","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-mega-stones"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\